descr: "The MeasureReport resource contains the results of evaluating a measure."

fields.name: identifier
fields.descr: "The identifier of the population group as defined in the measure definition."

fields.name: population
fields.descr: "The populations that make up the population group, one for each type of population appropriate for the measure."

fields.name: measureScore
fields.descr: "The measure score for this population group, calculated as appropriate for the measure type and scoring method, and based on the contents of the populations defined in the group."

fields.name: stratifier
fields.descr: "When a measure includes multiple stratifiers, there will be a stratifier group for each stratifier defined by the measure."
